      "content": "Wait, so you're saying you gave the hardest routes to certain groups because they had \"higher tenure\"? That feels like you're just using their loyalty to exploit them. If EquiRoute is going to force a redistribution so everyone gets a fair shot, won't that actually mess up the efficiency and retention scores you're talking about? We need to know if replacing you will actually cause a total breakdown in the supply chain.",
